    "body": "Attached are some screenshots from TD and RA demostrating the issue. The screenshots are from replays but in the case of RA - I saw it ingame.\r\n\r\nFirst is TD (playtest-20170902): Two engies capture an airstrip, after selling there is nothing to provide vision but the building remains frozen under the fog.\r\n\r\n![openra-2017-09-23t165351412z](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1355810/30775386-0f91909a-a09b-11e7-94c8-e7b878f7adcf.png)\r\n![openra-2017-09-23t165351412z2](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1355810/30775385-0f9043ac-a09b-11e7-9771-3f72cec391ec.png)\r\n![openra-2017-09-23t165351412z3](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1355810/30775384-0f8838c4-a09b-11e7-9e9e-f3224c443c53.png)\r\n\r\nSecond example is with an oil derick in RA (release-20170527). It gets destroyed while I have no other vision there but remains frozen under the fog.\r\n\r\n![openra-2017-09-23t165351412z4](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1355810/30775399-3cb80342-a09b-11e7-8c1d-b038b509b1f0.png)\r\n![openra-2017-09-23t165351412z5](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1355810/30775400-3cbbecd2-a09b-11e7-8522-98545d5fc4a6.png)\r\n"
